data.description: Don't miss your chance to own a GORGEOUS & perfectly UPGRADED pool home in the highly sought after gated community of Campanilla!  Your new home features an open, light and bright floor plan and a stunning lushly landscaped wrap around yard featuring a built-in BBQ with refrigerator, a serene pool with cascading waterfall, fire pit, dog run with a french drainage system, outdoor shower, beautiful pergolas and custom gates.  The kitchen was recently fully remodeled with waterfall edge Quartz counters, bar seating, a custom hood & lighting, copper sink, self-closing drawers, and has a walk-in pantry.  Adjacent to the kitchen is the open concept dining and family room with a cozy fireplace and there's also a coat closet & powder bath downstairs.  There are 3 bedrooms upstairs, a loft with ceiling speakers (could be a 4th bedroom) and a laundry room.  The spacious primary bedroom has TWO walk-in cedar lined closets with custom cabinetry, a modern barn door separating the bedroom and the magazine worthy bathroom which has been recently remodeled as well with custom cabinetry, dual sinks, quartz counters, custom lighting, and a spacious walk-in shower. The secondary bedrooms have custom closet organizers and the upstairs hall bathroom is nicely upgraded. Complete with a tankless water heater and soft water system.  This home is located at the end of a cul-de-sac and has a 2 car garage with overhead storage.  Situated in the rolling hills of charming San Juan Capistrano, close to the quaint & historic SJC downtown, local parks, beaches and is freeway close!  Neighborhood amenities include hiking/biking trails, pickleball courts, sand volleyball court, picnic area and a kids playground. And to top things off....the HOA dues are LOW and there are NO Mello Roos!
